data.name: unpackingRichTextBox.Text
data.value: - Make sure you have at least 1 GB free memory space if you want unpack all files - Choose Taz Pak files (pc, xpb, ps2) on the first file dialog and output folder the on second - This process can take some time ... - Use specific tools to open and edit media files (Raw bitmap editors, vgmstream, ...)
